item.dc:creator: @fireman7778 fireman7778
item.description:
@fireman7778 wrote:

ok, firstly u say it goes to winrar, so where ever you saved you’re source, you should see (for me its a pile of books) and it should have the name of the source.
now right click on whatever your source is, which should be a book looking thing
now click extract to specified folder
now you should get a yellow folder under this or above depending on your computer
now just open up the folder and you should see things like, client.java, autospawn
mainly just a bunch of folders,
now for most editing go to the tutorial section
also if its not working
download
Mod Taharoks
server source builder.
cant remember url
then pick a source you like and follow the steps above
